Rip notes: Nothing Was Ripped

American football gets the Dreamcast treatment in this game brought to you by Acclaim.

Choose from Exhibition/Season/Playoff modes, or try to change the out come of 33 Super Bowls from the past in the Historical Sim mode. Theres also support for upto 4
players.

You can customise all aspects of your team including Offence/Defence plays, squad line ups, or create your own players and team from scratch, allowing you to take on the whole of the NFL or re-write Super Bowl history.